ed by metal-free gas. Measuring the volume filling fractions of\nthis metal-free phase can constrain metal mixing parameters and Pop III star\nformation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Jun 2020 02:30:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Jul 2020 13:50:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-29"}
